parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission delay and failure can cause the vehicle to hesitate or stall, leading to accidents or loss of control, especially when reversing or merging onto a highway.
symptoms: Delayed engagement of reverse gear
hesitation or stalling when shifting gears
rough shifting
loss of power
and error messages on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The powertrain failure and malfunction can cause the vehicle to lose power, hesitate, or stall, leading to accidents or loss of control, especially when driving at high speeds.
symptoms: Loss of power
hesitation
stalling
error messages on the dashboard
and unusual noises or vibrations.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The back over prevention system failure can cause the vehicle to roll or move unexpectedly, leading to accidents or injuries, especially when reversing.
symptoms: Delayed or failed engagement of reverse gear
gray or blue screen on the back over prevention camera
and unexpected movement of the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Recall Repair Delays and Parts Unavailability
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delay in recall repairs and unavailability of parts can cause owners to continue driving vehicles with known safety issues, increasing the risk of accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Notification of recall
but no available parts or repair appointments
and continued driving with known safety issues.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rearview camera can cause accidents or injuries while reversing, as the driver may not have a clear view of the surroundings.
symptoms: The rearview camera displays a delayed or distorted image
the camera fails to display an image
the camera freezes or shows an incorrect distance to obstacles.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause various safety features to malfunction, including the air conditioning, power lift gate, and advanced driver-assistance systems (ADAS), which can lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The air conditioning blows hot air
the power lift gate opens and closes randomly
the ADAS features malfunction
the vehicle's electrical system causes errors or failures.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Vehicle Stalling or Loss of Power
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The stalling or loss of power can cause accidents or leave the driver stranded, especially if it occurs while driving at high speeds.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or loses power
the vehicle's engine hot warning message appears on the instrument panel
the vehicle's electrical system causes errors or failures.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system can cause accidents or injuries, as the vehicle may not stop properly or may roll forward unexpectedly.
symptoms: The vehicle rolls forward while the brake pedal is applied
the brake pedal has a delayed or soft response.
